decks.notes: The key concept of the deck is to use instant reanimation spells like Goryo's Vengeance and Fable of the Mirror-Breaker to quickly bring powerful creatures like Griselbrand and Atraxa, Grand Unifier onto the battlefield. These creatures, along with Territorial Kavu, Djeru and Hazoret, provide aggressive damage and board control. The deck also utilizes Fury of the Horde as a way to get additional combat steps and attack multiple times in a turn. The mana base includes a variety of fetchlands and shocklands to ensure consistent mana fixing. The deck aims to win the game quickly by combining these elements of reanimation and aggression.
